Where ArgoCD Runs
ArgoCD is not usually installed on the Jenkins slave node.
Typical setup:
EC2-1  -> Jenkins
EC2-2  -> Jenkins Agent
EC2-3  -> Kubernetes Cluster (or EKS)
            |
            └── ArgoCD installed inside Kubernetes
ArgoCD continuously watches the Git repository and automatically deploys any manifest changes.
